UnsupportedSyntax

  x Type assertions that would change binary expression grouping are not supported in strip-only mode.
   ,----
 1 | 1 ** 1 as number ** 2;
   : ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
   `----
UnsupportedSyntax

  x Type assertions that would change binary expression grouping are not supported in strip-only mode.
   ,-[3:1]
 2 | 
 3 | 1 ** 1 as const ** 2;
   : ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
   `----
